"...The cross of our Lord Jesus Christ..." (Galatians 6:1 4).
Ballington Booth Arr. by F. E. B.
"Will you follow the promptings of an unsanctified heart, turn away from self-denial for Christ's sake, and step over the cross without lifting it?
that you may place a true estimate upon eternal things."
Or will you lift that cross, heavy though it may be, and make some sacrifice for the truth's sake? May God help you to see where you are,
